videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield pulls up from way downtown and swishes the 3-point attempt.
videos.headline: Dangerfield drops in deep 3-pointer

videos.description: UConn's Megan Walker sends a pass behind the defense to a driving Christyn Williams, who finishes with a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Walker finds Williams perfectly for layup) 2020/01/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Walker finds Williams perfectly for layup

videos.description: Baylor's Te'a Cooper grabs the defensive rebound and flies all the way to the basket for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Baylor's Cooper goes coast-to-coast for the layup) 2020/01/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Cooper goes coast-to-coast for the layup

videos.description: UConn's Megan Walker drains a 3-pointer from the corner and then comes up with a steal on defense, in which she flies to the rim for a layup and a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Walker hits 3-pointer, follows up with steal plus and-1) 2020/01/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Walker hits 3-pointer, follows up with steal plus and-1

videos.description: UConn's Christyn Williams drives in towards the basket and drops in a tough jumper while drawing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Williams drives in for tough and-1) 2020/01/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Williams drives in for tough and-1

videos.description: Baylor's Lauren Cox passes to Te'a Cooper in the corner and she knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Baylor's Cooper hits 3-pointer from the corner) 2020/01/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Cooper hits 3-pointer from the corner

videos.description: Baylor's NaLyssa Smith flies in for the easy layup and Geno Auriemma is forced to call a timeout for UConn and he doesn't look happy.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Auriemma not happy after Smith hits layup for Baylor) 2020/01/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auriemma not happy after Smith hits layup for Baylor
